title: Binimoto Sushi
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Japanese, Fast food, Delivery, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Sushi place selling pre-prepared bento boxes. The box number 5 povrce, povrce (vegetables, vegetables), is vegan and contains 2 avocado hosomaki, 2 cucumber (kappa) hosomaki, 2 carrot hosomaki, 2 roasted pepper nigiri, 2 asparagus nigiri and 2 pepper-avocado-ginger-chard-carrot-cucumber uramaki. Non-smoking.
